Building out-of-sourcedir on Linux
----------------------------------

set JAVA_HOME, e.g. :

export JAVA_HOME="$(readlink -e $(which java) | sed s/\\/jre\\/bin\\/java//)"

32bit Linux:

mkdir build ; cd build ; qmake CONFIG+=release ../launcher.pro ; make ; cd ..

64 bit (qmake seems to need some proding) Linux:

mkdir build ; cd build ; qmake CONFIG+=release -spec linux-g++-64 ../launcher.pro ; make ; cd ..

OSX:

mkdir build && cd build && qmake CONFIG+=release -spec /usr/local/opt/qt/mkspecs/macx-g++ ../launcher.pro && make
